Dialogs.Dialog: Did you wait？ It's raining, isn't it？
I just got here. Well, the weather's not helping.
Sorry to keep you waiting. I'm glad you're here first. It's too cold today.
You're right on time. It would be great if it wasn't raining.
It's nice to have this once in a while.
Yes, right on time. I thought you would be late because of the snow.
I'm not going to leave you waiting that much.
I'm late！ Sorry about the rain.
Hah, a healthy Rinko waiting in the snow...
How long are you going to make me wait in the rain？
I'm so sorry！ Won't happen again！
Too late！ I can't believe you made me wait so long in the snow.
I'm really sorry... Thanks for waiting.
(Oh, by the way, don't we have a date today！ No way...)
Hah... Why are you still at home...
(Oh, by the way, don't we have a date today！ No way...)
You're here... How could you forget？
(Oh, by the way, don't we have a date today！ No way...)
I was wondering if I could join you on the way here... But now we're here.
Excuse me. I'm trying to get to the location of this map...
Oh, is it a road？ Let's see... If it's here, go straight on this road and go to the first traffic light at...
Kidding. I saw that. You did good.
(I'm a little early for our appointment.)
Here, look, I won！ One more drink, ▲小早川＊▲！
Heh, lucky you. Well, thanks for the drink.
Rinko just arrived, you've been here a while ▲主人公＊▲？
No, I just arrived too. We seem to be more in sync than usual today！
Then why don't we play rock-paper-scissors？ If you don't get a win, you get a kick as punishment！
Hey, have you seen a cat？
I saw her on the way here and chased after her, but I lost her. Ahh.
Haha, well maybe it'll come up again eventually.
(I'm a little late... Huh, there's something wrong with you, ▲小早川＊▲.)
What's with the face？ Are you standing on your toes, ▲小早川＊▲？
Ah this, muscle training. Sort of.
Heh, you want to keep going？
Well, until I get tired of it.
(I think I'm going to get tired of it pretty soon...)
(Scurrying like this makes me feel like I want to protect you, ▲小早川＊▲.)
I take back what I said before！
What are you talking about？ You're late.
(Oh no... I'm pretty late. Ah, ▲小早川＊▲？)
(Talking to a guy...？ Oh... he's gone.)
Sorry, who was that you were just talking to？ A friend？
No, a pick-up. And he's in middle school！ "Where are you going？" He said. Don't make fun of me.
(Did they think you were a middle schooler...？)
Huh, did you just arrive, ▲小早川＊▲？
Why did you do that, ▲小早川＊▲！？
I thought I'd kick you if you forgot.
From the looks of it, I guess you did remember. Hah...
Just hurry up and get ready.
Oh, it's okay now. You can get out.
I see. Geez, I was worried about you.
(It's cloudy today, but this is about right...)
Hey, it's kind of dreary weather...
I know, right？ I hope it will clear up quickly.
Sorry to keep you waiting. The weather is not so clear. Rinko likes it this way, though.
Did you wait for me ▲主人公＊▲？
Nope. It's more of a subtle cloudburst. The chance of precipitation was also subtle.
My neighbor's cat didn't wash her face, so I don't think it'll be fine. Because that girl's forecast is always right.
Ah, the rain is amazing, ▲小早川＊▲！
We should take shelter from the rain somewhere...
I don't mind, but holding an umbrella is a hassle.
Is that a... far-fetched cue to share an umbrella？
Ouch, I slipped in the snow...
It was a clean tumble, so contrived！
Did I make you wait, ▲小早川＊▲？
I just got here. Did you notice the little snowman over there？
Oh, it's true. It has a face and arms for such a small size. They are so dexterous in making it.
I'm gonna go take some pictures... wait here！
What's wrong？ Did something happen ▲小早川＊▲！？
It was windy and my skirt was...
Yeah... I'm fine. I just got pushed around by the wind.
You look like you have something to complain about... I'm not sure.
This is... from last time. Hehe, I put it on.
I liked it so much, so I put it back on.
I was in the mood, so I put on this as a present.
Really？ Hehe. Then it's going to be in heavy rotation for the time being.
Yeah, Rinko thinks it's pretty good too.
Wait. Aren't you impressed or something？
How do you like my hair？
Why don't you try a new haircut？
Why don't you try changing its hair color？
Why don't you try changing the length of your hair？
That might be a good idea. I'll think about it.
I see... Rinko likes it a lot though.
...Say what you want to say clearly.
What is it？ I wouldn't know if you don't say anything.
What！？ I just changed it the other day.
Yes, yes. You don't have to say what you think.
Hey. My hair has grown long lately. How do you like it？
You're not going to cut it？
I see, good. Rinko was thinking of growing it as well.
You want it short？ Well, okay.
No way, you did not realize？ ...It can't be, right？
What do you think of this haircut？
How do you like the color of my hair？
Um... what do you think of this hair color？ Come on, be frank.
Really？ You like this kind of thing？ I'll keep that in mind.
Ehhh... I see... you don't like it.
Yes, yes. I'm done talking about this.
I'm hungry. What are you going to do for lunch？
I'm hungry. I might not make it.
Come to think of it, I might be getting a little hungry.
Yeah. Well, I'll just leave it at that.
Look, there's a break in the clouds. It looks like the weather is getting better.
The sky is looking a bit iffy. I hope it stays cloudy.
Snow... Look, look, look. It's coming down.
It seems to be raining outside. It's going to be pretty strong, isn't it？
Seems like it. Well then, let's hurry up.
Wait, it's coming down. It's going to get stronger, isn't it？
It's true. Maybe we should reschedule...
Yeah, okay. If you decided that, let's get going.
Ah... you're making that face again...
Yeah... I wonder if Rinko feels the same way.
You should care about your surroundings.
I said no. Look... there are people.
Rinko's not in the mood for this.
Huh？ Ah... you're tilting the umbrella.
Hey！ It's enough that you are attached to me like this.
It's going to rain, you know.
Well, okay, but don't suck at it.
Rinko is the model, so don't be out of focus or anything.
Hehe, take a good shot, will you？
I don't want to. I don't like it, so I don't want to.
Would you like something light to eat？
I'm hungry... It' s a good time, how about lunch？
It's almost time for dinner. Do you want to go out somewhere to eat？
Yeah, that's good. Rinko is getting hungry too.
Sure. If you want to go, I'll go with you.
What a bother. Rinko's not hungry.
Are we there already？ Did you know we were this close？
When we talk, time passes by fast.
Come on, we' re heading off.
...both of us brought our umbrellas. We are a well- prepared couple.
Rinko should have intentionally left her umbrella behind.
Don't you have an umbrella？ I have no choice... come here.
Oh, thank you. Well then, I'll hold your umbrella.
Did you forget your umbrella？ Come on, get under mine.
Here's your umbrella. Aren't you happy to be able to share an umbrella with Rinko？
Oh, thank you. I was lucky to forget it.
Here, an umbrella. You don't have one, do you？
Here, why don't you get under the umbrella？
...I have no choice. Don't get too close.
Come on, get under the umbrella. You don't have one, do you？
Yes. Hehe... I'm glad I forgot.
Don't you have an umbrella？ I forgot mine too...
Well, let's hurry up and go.
I see... I don't mind, though.
Are you thinking about getting close to Rinko now？
...I think we're more like lovers this way...
...It's good, right？ This one is better.
Squeeze！ I wanted to try saying that... Hehe.
Um... sorry, I made a mistake.
I don't know what you're doing. Well, I'm okay here, too.
(If that's what you want, then it's all fine, ▲小早川＊▲...)
...hey. You know what, is this the right place？
...Oh, I must have made a mistake.
Hah, I have no choice. We're running out of time, so let's just stay here.
(If that's what you want, then it's all fine, ▲小早川＊▲...)
Now, which game shall we play？
Hey, which one do you want？
Why don't you pick the one you like？
Hey, hey？ Let's play some more.
Well, it was interesting. Do you want to try the other ones？
Sorry to be so bossy, but... Rinko'd like to go somewhere else soon.
I'm kind of getting tired of it...
Um... I brought a bento, what do you want to do？
Of course, I'll wanna eat. Lucky me！
In case you're wondering, I made a bento for you. If you don't want it, that's fine.
You know what, I made you a bento. You'll eat it, right？
Then, do you want to come to my house？
Do you want to do it here？
I'm not in the mood for that.
You have lint on it. Come on, crouch！
I said "good morning" to a neighborhood elementary school kid this morning and he ignored me...
Are they telling students at school not to respond unnecessarily？
Why don't you just be flexible when you see who you're dealing with？ I mean, you're dealing with a nice high school girl. Kids these days...
But you were like that until we started dating...
Did you see the special that was on last night？
Oh, the two-hour quiz show？ I was going to watch it, but ended up forgetting about it.
It's totally boring. I didn't understand why it was so popular even though I watched it all the way through.
(You watched it all the way through...)
What's that？ You sound like an old man.
Hehe, I hope it's not a bad rumor.
Rinko's classmate... I see. I'm not sure if they're dating or not.
Heh, don't go around telling everyone about it, okay？
...The twins over there, they look so much alike. Hey, what if Rinko had a twin？
It would be tough if you did, don't you think so ▲小早川＊▲？
What do you mean？ Don't you think, "I want to go out with you two" or something like that？
Ah, a beautiful cat. This is not a stray.
Can you tell？ I'm not sure how can you do that.
You can tell by looking at the fur and the luster. You're not ready yet.
I've been playing Volvavin with my little brother for a bit. Child's play is tough.
Uh... my stomach hurts a little.
Eh... are you okay？ You need to rest somewhere？
Hmm, I'll probably be fine. It's a common one, so just wait and it will be fine.
That's okay, but if it's hard for you, just tell me, okay？
Hmm, really. Shall we say hello？
It's okay, it's going to be a quack. Look, they'll know if you stare at them.
(Do you have that much of a guilty conscience...？)
We haven't had lunch yet. Do you wanna eat somewhere？
Isn't it about time for dinner？ What do you say？
You know... this is Rinko's special bento box. Do you want some？
Of course I'm going to eat it！
It's not even noon yet. Can we spend a little more time together？
It's a little early, isn't it？ Let's play some more.
Are you still okay with the time？ I'd like to stay with you a little longer.
Of course. Even Rinko wants to stay with you.
I'm glad. So where do we go next？
Yeah. Rinko also thought you wanted to be together some more.
see. Where do you want to go then？
I'd love to play some more, but... I have plans after this.
I see. Then it's time to go...
Even Rinko wanted to spend some more time, but... time.
...No thanks. Let's stop for the day.
Rinko's not free today. I'm going home.
I guess I don't have a choice...
Then, do you want to my house？
Do you want to go here？
You know... can I lean on you？
Hey, can I lean on you？
...Maybe I'll always want to do this.
Did I miss the ride？ And now... let's get off.
Come on, we have to get off.
We're almost there, you have to wake up, ▲小早川＊▲.
...Hmm？ I wanted to sleep a little longer...
Are you tired？ You can lean back.
Yeah. I'm a little tired, so I'll take on your offer...
Nope... I'm not in the mood.
I have no choice, since you look so lonely.
If the train didn't stop, we... could do this all the time.
You can always lean on me.
Would you like to come by my house？ I'd like to spend a little more time with you.
Your house... huh. Yeah, that would be nice.
Sounds good. I'll come by then.
You know, I'd like to spend a little more time with you... can we go to your house？
And I'd like to be with you as long as possible.
Actually, I have a present for you.
Why don't we just do it the next time we see each other？ See you.
Eh, a pleasure？ S-See you. Bye-bye！
Oh... I don't have a key to the house.
What, you don't have it in your bag？ What about your pockets？
Pockets？ Um... oh, here it is！ I was worried...
Haha, I was worried, too. See you later.
Hey, if you want, do you want to come over？ I don't know if my little brother will be too noisy, though.
And while you're at it, why don't you come on up？ My family's not here, so it'll be quiet.
Are you sure？ Then let's do it
Yeah, thank you for inviting me.
I see... Well, I'll see you soon.
I'm sorry you had to go through the trouble of inviting me.
I wish I could just live here... Hehe, I'm kidding.
Thanks, it was fun. See you soon.
Did I annoy you in some way by making you stay？ ...See you.
You know... I had a good time today. Sorry.
I'm glad to hear that. I'm sorry I wasn't more considerate before.
No, I'm glad we made up. I look forward to seeing you again in the future.
Um, I'm... sorry about the other night. Did we make up... on this date？
Yes, we did. I'll be more careful from now on.
Hehe... Thanks. Well, I'll look forward to our next date.
Yeah, let's have another fun date. See you.
I'm sorry about that. Can you forgive Rinko already？
Don't worry about it. It's not your fault either.
Good！ Let's go on another date then, shall we？ Thanks for today. Bye-bye.
